{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 \b \fs36 Consolidate OMF to RPP via AATranslator\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 This is a highly specific script. The workflow is as follows:\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab {\b outside Reaper}\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li720 \fi-360 1.\tx360\tab create a new folder\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li720 \fi-360 2.\tx360\tab convert your individual OMF files to individual RPP sessions\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li720 \fi-360 3.\tx360\tab move the individual RPP sessions and the corresponding video files inside your folder\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li720 \fi-360 4.\tx360\tab copy the {\i /path/to/your/folder} to the clipboard\sa180\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab {\b inside Reaper}\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li720 \fi-360 1.\tx360\tab launch the script\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li720 \fi-360 2.\tx360\tab paste {\i /path/to/your/folder} in the dialog\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li720 \fi-360 3.\tx360\tab reaper will now close all your open sessions (will ask to save or not)\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li720 \fi-360 4.\tx360\tab reaper creates a {\i consolidate.RPP} session\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li720 \fi-360 5.\tx360\tab reaper opens every individual RPP session as a tab\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li1080 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab imports the video to this session\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li1080 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab copy and pastes all tracks from each session to the {\i consolidate.RPP} session with a time offset\sa180\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li720 \fi-360 6.\tx360\tab reaper merges all {\b same named tracks} in the {\i consolidate.RPP} session\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li720 \fi-360 7.\tx360\tab reaper deletes all tracks without items on it\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li720 \fi-360 8.\tx360\tab reaper creates named regions for each {\b videofile}\sa180\sa180\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 \b \fs36 TODO\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab prompt for ffmpeg video convert\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab prompt for automation removal\sa180\par}
